      <trans-unit id="15569" identifier="835316aaaf899e1b11de795ef4c4c92f">
        <source>Set up a line of cards, with the animal facing upwards.</source>
        <target>crwdns15569:0crwdne15569:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[8]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="11759" identifier="bfaf38b7e602d0e29e44094685c84dbf">
        <source>Have a payment system ready such as tokens for your classroom, counters, sweets, or marbles.</source>
        <target>crwdns11759:0crwdne11759:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ol/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15570" identifier="71937c249bd4fe14db71a4cc4662069a">
        <source>The game is even better if you have some real stakes - for example: I have 10 marbles each is worth 2 minutes of game time.</source>
        <target>crwdns15570:0crwdne15570:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[9]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15571" identifier="5a84f584c4a27f0731a0db94adcce1a0">
        <source>For every token you use to find the number I’m thinking of, you will lose a marble.</source>
        <target>crwdns15571:0crwdne15571:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[9]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15572" identifier="1c8fe226da34611c9dd32f911757c2d8">
        <source>Let’s see how many guesses it takes to find the number: 302</source>
        <target>crwdns15572:0crwdne15572:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[10]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15573" identifier="5e4dc264c60f4033b14b110c9ed06577">
        <source>{image file-path=&quot;img/topics/cards-1.png&quot; alt=&quot;A line of cards, middle one selected.&quot;}</source>
        <target>crwdns15573:0crwdne15573:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[11]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15574" identifier="bd3c1d2240602cc708cc8a823f7ac8c3">
        <source>Who would like the first guess?</source>
        <target>crwdns15574:0crwdne15574:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15575" identifier="75b35f68fdff96587cbb74084c537cfa">
        <source>(Choose a student).</source>
        <target>crwdns15575:0crwdne15575:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15576" identifier="fd4734b0e2b336553f6a400c23d4b16e">
        <source>Which animal should I turn over?</source>
        <target>crwdns15576:0crwdne15576:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15577" identifier="ca5587e509947cde0bd311ad51dd64ba">
        <source>Tell us why you chose that guess.</source>
        <target>crwdns15577:0crwdne15577:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15578" identifier="cccc743be6d891e3b2339717251c0fb0">
        <source>(They should be selecting the card that is exactly half way.</source>
        <target>crwdns15578:0crwdne15578:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15579" identifier="0ef661c0c670712a8a30f2e22595b46e">
        <source>If they didn’t, check with the class if they agree with the choice or could they add to the student’s thinking to select the middle card.</source>
        <target>crwdns15579:0crwdne15579:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15580" identifier="a78ab4b8e8756ba656839051e888a201">
        <source>If they decide not to, that's fine; they will learn the hard way if they use a less efficient approach.)</source>
        <target>crwdns15580:0crwdne15580:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[12]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15581" identifier="acbbccb442d335ab776cc5b3c8e0d1cb">
        <source>Turn over the chosen card to show the number under it.</source>
        <target>crwdns15581:0crwdne15581:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[13]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15582" identifier="e7708d67eac61dad98f2c26d9d8cbec2">
        <source>If it's the correct one, you can stop, otherwise &lt;em&gt;remove that card and all other cards that the number can’t be&lt;/em&gt; (which will either be all cards to the right or all cards to the left of the chosen one) and take away one token from your pile.</source>
        <target>crwdns15582:0crwdne15582:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[13]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15583" identifier="a4868c763eaac221bc6b09c21b8669a9">
        <source>Repeat this process until a student chooses the card with your number on it; if they use all ten tokens then the teacher &quot;wins&quot;.</source>
        <target>crwdns15583:0crwdne15583:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[13]</note>
      </trans-unit>
