        <target>crwdns15585:0crwdne15585:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[15]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15586" identifier="2d4238c4ae62f29447095661daf86d61">
        <source>{image file-path=&quot;img/topics/cards-4.png&quot; alt=&quot;Correct card selected.&quot;}</source>
        <target>crwdns15586:0crwdne15586:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[16]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15587" identifier="9617eee8d7bed5d26b681a8e9621536f">
        <source>How many guesses did it take to find the number?</source>
        <target>crwdns15587:0crwdne15587:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[17]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15588" identifier="77836669b5ceb89b72693085346c4170">
        <source>With each guess, how many cards were eliminated from being a possibility?
(Answer: half the cards could be eliminated with each guess if you picked the middle card. )</source>
        <target>crwdns15588:0crwdne15588:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[18]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15589" identifier="90267d0382c15d13194a8be60ca184bf">
        <source>Did the students win because they guessed within 10  guesses or did you win because it took them longer?</source>
        <target>crwdns15589:0crwdne15589:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[19]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15590" identifier="8a71af0fb00d5fc538b6b0fbcaaab006">
        <source>Repeat this game until the students have won 3 times or you have won 3 times.</source>
        <target>crwdns15590:0crwdne15590:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[20]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15591" identifier="91459119fbe8d6c103e9378044a708f2">
        <source>{panel type=&quot;teaching&quot; title=&quot;Teaching observations&quot;}</source>
        <target>crwdns15591:0crwdne15591:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[21]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15592" identifier="5ba10dad6c465bd20ac68908c2278ba2">
        <source>The number of guesses required can be anything from 1 (if you are lucky the first time), to 5 (if you have chosen the middle number each time).</source>
        <target>crwdns15592:0crwdne15592:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[22]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15593" identifier="1cf39a4f4b8e3d51936e43a7b7f10520">
        <source>Of course, they may use more than 5 guesses if they use a poor strategy.</source>
        <target>crwdns15593:0crwdne15593:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[22]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15594" identifier="ccaf417c740db8f24ef0c4a249ea7732">
        <source>Most of the time they will need close to 5 guesses.</source>
        <target>crwdns15594:0crwdne15594:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[22]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15595" identifier="1de884f368646aef680e34f5a008350c">
        <source>This also means that students will always have tokens left if they use a good strategy, since the maximum number of guesses to find the number is 5.</source>
        <target>crwdns15595:0crwdne15595:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[22]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="15596" identifier="59e042da1872bd44e9c06a8263fafdde">
